abstract: A small search engine accused Google of raising its ad rates after it realized the company was a potential competitor.
snippet: A small search engine accused Google of raising its ad rates after it realized the company was a potential competitor.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO  A small Web site operator filed an antitrust suit against Google on Tuesday, accusing it of unfairly manipulating its advertising system to harm a potential competitor.

headline.main: Lawsuit Says Google Was Unfair to Rival Site
headline.print_headline: Lawsuit Says Google Was Unfair To Rival Site
